[chuckles]What can I say?

00:53.219 --> 00:56.598
I know how to deal with eventhe most troublesome travelers.

00:57.265 --> 00:58.933
Wow! What is the rush?

00:59.017 --> 01:01.102
'I never understandwhy people get so crazy'

01:01.144 --> 01:02.395
at this time of year.

01:02.479 --> 01:04.772
Uh, maybe 'cause not everyonejets off

01:04.772 --> 01:07.192
to some amazing cornerof the world every Christmas.

01:07.233 --> 01:08.610
I mean, what is itfor you this year

01:08.693 --> 01:10.695
jingle bells in Jamaica, or..

01:10.737 --> 01:12.447
No. It's fruitcake in Finland.

01:12.530 --> 01:14.908
- A bikini in Bali.- 'Ah!'

01:14.991 --> 01:16.493
[laughs]

01:16.618 --> 01:17.952
I know, all I have to dois just make

01:18.078 --> 01:19.954
a few tight connectionsafter this last flight

01:19.954 --> 01:23.249
and I will be on a white,sandy beach until New Year's.

01:23.291 --> 01:25.126
You're my hero, I think.

01:25.168 --> 01:27.420
[laughs]Why not?

01:27.462 --> 01:29.130
A book and a beach chairin the tropics

01:29.130 --> 01:31.382
suits me just fine.

01:31.424 --> 01:32.717
Oh, boy!

01:32.759 --> 01:35.637
Oh. I think we shouldcatch our flights.

01:36.888 --> 01:37.972
Taxi!

01:39.641 --> 01:42.936
[instrumental music]

01:51.820 --> 01:55.406
- Hi, Ted. I'm here for 3:25.- Great! Sydney.

01:55.490 --> 01:57.575
You have an unaccompanied minorinto Chicago.

01:57.659 --> 01:59.994
- Uh, she just cleared security.- Okay, great. Thanks.

01:59.994 --> 02:03.665
By the way, my spies in HRsaid your interview went great.

02:03.790 --> 02:05.083
[gasps]Fingers crossed.

02:05.166 --> 02:06.793
I know they're gonna makethe decision soon.

02:06.835 --> 02:09.711
A posting in Rome would open upa whole new continent to you.

02:09.753 --> 02:11.339
Let's just hopethat my dream job

02:11.339 --> 02:13.174
isn't just a dream, you know?

02:13.299 --> 02:14.592
I mean, everybody wants Rome.

02:14.634 --> 02:16.886
Yeah, but not everybody'slearning Italian

02:17.011 --> 02:17.846
and working as hard.

02:18.012 --> 02:19.931
I mean, if anyone deserves it,it's you.

02:20.014 --> 02:23.643
Kerry, if I don't see youbefore Bali, Merry Christmas.

02:23.726 --> 02:24.811
Same here, think of me

02:24.894 --> 02:26.855
when you're relaxingon some tropical beach

02:26.938 --> 02:29.524
and I'm working the red-eyeto Topeka.

02:29.607 --> 02:31.151
[both chuckling]

02:31.192 --> 02:33.069
- Aw.- See you soon.

02:33.194 --> 02:34.279
- You bet.- Okay.

02:34.362 --> 02:36.114
- Safe travels.- Thank you.

02:36.197 --> 02:38.199
Thanks, Ted.

02:38.199 --> 02:41.286
